  "text": "This study was conducted at the Haibei Alpine Meadow Ecosystem Research Station (latitude: 37°37 0 N, longitude: 101°12 0 E, elevation: 3200 m), which has a continental monsoon climate with severe, long winters and short, cool summers. The mean annual temperature and precipitation are 1.6°C and 562 mm, respectively, and over 80% of the precipitation falls during the summer monsoon season [CITATION_1] . Mean temperature and total rainfall were 8.9 and 8.1°C and 412.6 and 307.8 mm during the growing seasons (May-September) in 2010 and 2011, respectively.",
